  07 Mar 2008; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org>
  postgresql-server-7.3.21.ebuild, postgresql-server-7.4.19.ebuild,
  postgresql-server-8.0.15.ebuild, postgresql-server-8.1.11.ebuild,
